<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Message Has Been Received | AlphaTech Multimedia</title>

    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3f4f6 0%, #e9ecf2 100%);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        color: #333;
      }

      .wrapper {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffffcc;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        border-radius: 20px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4B0082, #DAA520);
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 25px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .header p {
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
        opacity: 0.95;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 17px;
        color: #222;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .message {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }

      .highlight-box {
        background: #fafaff;
        border: 1px solid #ebe7ff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 18px 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .highlight-box strong {
        color: #4B0082;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4B0082, #DAA520);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 14px 26px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .footer {
        background: #f9f9fb;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 24px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #666;
      }

      .footer strong {
        color: #4B0082;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #DAA520;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 6px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
          padding: 12px 22px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Thank You for Reaching Out!</h1>
        <p>We've successfully received your message at AlphaTech Multimedia</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p class="greeting">Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        <p class="message">
          We truly appreciate you contacting us. Our support team has received your message
          regarding <strong><%= subject %></strong>, and we’ll get back to you as soon as possible.
          In the meantime, you can review your message details below:
        </p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          <p><strong>Your Message:</strong></p>
          <div style="margin-top:8px;">
            <%- message
              .split(/\n\s*\n/)
              .map(p => `<p style="margin:0 0 10px 0;">${p.trim().replace(/\n/g, '<br>')}</p>`)
              .join('') %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="message">
          If this inquiry is urgent, please don’t hesitate to reach out directly via email or phone.
        </p>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 35px;">
          <a href="<%= site_url %>" class="cta-button">Visit Our Website</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <strong><%= site_name %></strong><br />
          You’re receiving this email because you contacted us via our website.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="<%= site_url %>">Home</a> |
          <a href="mailto:<%= contact_email %>">Contact Support</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
